{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the shadowed veil between life and death in <i>Deadman\u2019s Pact</i>, a fast-paced, arcade style, action-platformer where every moment matters and every soul reclaimed fuels your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979430/extras/Filler1.png?t=1733833805\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face hordes of enemies corrupted by dark forces, traverse treacherous landscapes, and master a fluid combat system powered by strategic combos and devastating finishers. The clock is always ticking, and the stakes grow higher with each passing second. Will you focus on the hunt for lost souls, or risk it all to fight back against increasingly powerful foes?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979430/extras/Filler1.png?t=1733833805\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adapt to escalating challenges as the enemies evolve and hazards multiply. Compete with friends or enemies for the highest score on over 15 unique levels.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979430/extras/Filler1.png?t=1733833805\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The only way forward is through. The Reaper is watching\u2014will you fulfill the pact.. or succumb to the void?  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979430/extras/Filler1.png?t=1733833805\" />\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00